OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784321281
OL,3,CFamily of mum, 24, stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cshe slept next to baby call for justice
OL,6,FKirandeep's mother, Baljeet Kaur, told
OL,7,FITV News: "We send them somewhere safe
OL,8,Fto study then this happens.
OL,10,F"We didn't realise hooliganism and
OL,11,Fviolence is happening there too.
OL,13,F"We want justice, we want our
OL,14,Fdaughter's body returned from Hayes."
OL,16,FKirandeep had been living in the UK
OL,17,Fsince 2024 on a student visa.
OL,19,FAfter completing her studies, she had
OL,20,Fbegun working and was looking forward
OL,21,Fto building a life in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
