OL,3,CFamily of mum, 24, stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cshe slept next to baby call for justice
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FKirandeep's brother, Gurvinder Singh,
OL,12,Fspoke of the family's devastation at
OL,13,Fhearing the news of her death.
OL,15,F"We found out today (Friday, July 17)
OL,16,Fthat she died," he said.
OL,18,F"We were shocked, we don't understand
OL,19,Fwhat we can do."
