PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784321281
OL,3,CFamily of mum, 24, stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cshe slept next to baby call for justice
OL,6,FMr Singh said the family don't have
OL,7,Fanyone who can bring her body back
OL,8,Fhome to their village in Punjab.
OL,10,FJassi Randhawa, a volunteer at a Hayes
OL,11,FSikh Gudwara, said Kirandeep's death
OL,12,Fwas a "big shock to the community" and
OL,13,Frecalled seeing her just weeks ago.
OL,15,FHe described her as "very nice, well-
OL,16,Fspoken" and "kind-hearted".
OL,18,FDaniel Sean James, 44, was charged
OL,19,Fwith murder, attempted murder and
OL,20,Fhaving a blade on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
